passport.intialize() = A middleware that intialize passport
passport.session() = A web application needs the ability to identify users as they browse from page to page. This series of requests and responses, each associated with the same user, is known as session

User.plugin(passportLocalMongoose);  //passportLocalMongoose automatically assigned username, password, salting and hashing we don't have to build from scratch


